<div>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color:black">Story in link has screenshots of the tweets. This is not the first reporter to get anti-Semitic threats after covering Trump. When asked about it previously Trump had &#8220;no message&#8221; for his supporters sending Ioffe
